===============================================================================
[ Examples ]

Example #1 hash_hmac() example

<?php >
  echo hash_hmac('sha256', 'The quick brown fox jumped over the lazy dog.', 
  'secret');
<?>

The above example will output:

9c5c42422b03f0ee32949920649445e417b2c634050833c5165704b825c2a53b

